      "title": "A special gazette was published",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has issued a special gazette bringing three more companies under the Ministry of Investment Promotion.",
        "Three major companies including Ragna Security Lanka Limited (RALL) have been brought under the Ministry of Investment Promotion.",
        "Selendiva Investments Limited and Hotel Developers (Lanka) Pvt Limited are two other companies brought under the Ministry of Investment Promotion.",
        "Earlier, Ragna Defense Lanka Company was under the Ministry of Defense and Selendiva Investments Ltd and Hotel Developers (Lanka) Pvt Ltd were under the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing."
      ],
